		"name": "Virtual Media",
		"description": "### Virtual Media API Postman Collection Overview\n\nThis collection is designed to test Redfish Virtual Media functionality, allowing remote media mounting and unmounting on a BMC (Baseboard Management Controller). It includes two key operations to simulate virtual media interaction typically used for remote boot or OS deployment scenarios.\n\n#### ðŸ”¹ **Collection Features**\n\n- ðŸ”¼ **InsertMedia**: Mount a virtual ISO image remotely using HTTPS stream transfer.\n    \n- ðŸ”½ **EjectMedia**: Unmount the currently inserted virtual media.\n    \n\n#### **Authentication**\n\nAll requests use HTTP Basic Authentication with:\n\n- **Username**: `Administrator`\n    \n- **Password**: `Password`\n    \n\n#### **Parameters Tested**\n\n- Image URL, credentials, and media attributes\n    \n\n#### **Intended Use**\n\n- BMC firmware testing\n    \n- Redfish VirtualMedia API validation\n    \n- Simulated OS or recovery media mounting",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
